{"tid":2269074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：須確保法援制度不被反共分子濫用 又指出暴動案脫罪不代表鬥爭停上","createTime":"2020-11-03T08:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T08:58:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"075e055b401f4e2b74e5344aa77e57dc3deec680","tid":2269074,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊：要確保法援制度的有限資源不被濫用<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊在「香港法律周」論壇上致辭表示，本港的法援制度相對其他司法管轄區寬鬆，相關開支並不設上限，過去10年本港的法援開支增加超過230%，認為要確保有限資源有效運用，<span class=\"gold\">防止有人濫用法援制度</span>。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊又指，本法的獨立司法制度世界知名，在去年世界經濟論壇及《全球競爭力報告》中排名亞洲第2及全球第8；《基本法》亦保障法院行使司法權時，是獨立、不受任何干預，但近日有涉及社會道德價值或政治爭議的個案被帶上法庭，<span class=\"gold\">她指雖然法庭會就申訴提出最終裁決，但反問爭議背後的價值觀及利益問題是否已經真正解決。</span><br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2364532&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=4685176e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364532</a>"},{"pid":"441f5f98e19daf1c2c9fb77c0adeabfedf9ccc8d","tid":2269074,"uid":225192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"世界知名 法治社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a25be4a538db997c32d7ba7b84b1fb80ccc8d7","tid":2269074,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"鬥爭思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbc1a7ebcf65e344bef51ab0a81d041d5becac3","tid":2269074,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"解決價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97fd4098960fbff6f81458df508ee6be8138e3d","tid":2269074,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"你地有得去英國<br />\n我無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}